  <script>
    $(".event-selection select").change(function(){
      $("#no-results").remove();
      var hide = true;
      if($(".event-selection select").val() == "ALL")  {
        $(".event").addClass("d-flex");
        $(".event").removeClass("d-none");
      } else  {
        $(".event").each(function()  {
          if($(this).data("category") != $(".event-selection select").val())  {
            $(this).removeClass("d-flex");
            $(this).addClass("d-none");
          } else {
            $(this).removeClass("d-none");
            $(this).addClass("d-flex");
            hide = false;
          }
        });
        if(hide)  {
          $("<div id='no-results' class='w-100 text-center py-5'><h11>No events coming up.<h11></div>").insertAfter(".event-selection");
        }  
      }
    });
    </script>

        <h7 class="event-date text-uppercase">Sat 01 Jun, 2019</h7>
        <h5 class="event-time text-uppercase">Gates Open 5:45 PM<br>Start time 7:25 PM</h5>
        <hr>
        <h6 class="event-title">Brisbane Lions v Hawthorn Football Club</h6>
